/* Feature Map: the versioned master catalog of what the app can do.
   This is the single source of truth for the feature map. Keep it current here
   as the app gains features: add or edit a card below, one object per capability.
   The in-app admin screen renders this and layers the admin's saved changes
   (hide / edit / add / reorder) on top as a preview; the public page renders this
   file directly with no login and no database. Plain JS, loaded via a normal
   <script> in index.html and listed in sw.js ASSETS (not the JSX loader).

   Card shape: { id, cat, role, name, summary, actions:[...], hidden? }
   - id:     stable slug, never reuse or change once shipped (admin overrides key on it)
   - role:   'user' (lifter) | 'coach' | 'both'
   - hidden: optional; true = kept in the catalog but not shown (curated out)
*/
